		<img width="2500" height="1200" src="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals.jpg" class="singlepostthumb wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals.jpg 2500w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals-520x250.jpg 520w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals-1200x576.jpg 1200w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals-768x369.jpg 768w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals-1536x737.jpg 1536w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals-2048x983.jpg 2048w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header-mining-seaweed-metals-900x432.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px" /><div class="post-thumbnail-caption">Scientists still have a lot to figure out, but the idea of sourcing critical minerals from seaweed is too tantalizing not to look into. Photo by Upix Photography/Alamy Stock Photo</div>
			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">What the Heck Is Seaweed Mining?</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Preliminary research suggests seaweed can trap and store valuable minerals. Is this the beginning of a new type of mining?</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/moira-donovan/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Moira Donovan</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						April 25, 2024 | 850 words, about 4 minutes
					</aside>

					
				</header>

				
