						<li>
							<a href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AWhat the Heck Is Seaweed Mining?%0D%0APreliminary research suggests seaweed can trap and store valuable minerals. Is this the beginning of a new type of mining?%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/what-the-heck-is-seaweed-mining/" title="Share by Email" target="_blank">
